NAME
    errors - Error Handling for Perl

STATUS
    This module is still being designed. Don't use it yet.

SYNOPSIS
        use errors;

        try {
            raise Error("Something is not cool")
                if $uncool;
        }
        except {
            warn $_;
        }
        finally {
            cleanup();
        };

DESCRIPTION
    Yet another attempt to add clean, sane, flexible and usable error
    handling to Perl.

